###
### 20. DEACTIVATE COMPANY - PATCH /api/companies/{id}/deactivate
###
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/companies/{{companyId}}/deactivate

###
### 21. DEACTIVATE COMPANY - Non-existent company
###
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/companies/99999/deactivate

###
### 22. DELETE COMPANY - DELETE /api/companies/{id}
###
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/companies/{{companyId}}
